        protected static java.io.File[] getDefaultScanDirs​(java.lang.String subdir,
                                                   boolean ignoreInternal)
        Returns an array of scanning directories based on the specified subdirectory using the result of ScanLayersService.getRootDirs() as the parent directories.
        Parameters:
        subdir - the subdirectory name to append to the known root directories.
        ignoreInternal - specify if internal directories should be ignored.
